body:
As a workaround, I added the following configuration.

```
  webpackFinal(config) {
      if(!config.resolve?.alias) return config
      config.resolve.alias = {
        ...config.resolve?.alias,
        "next/link": "next/dist/client/app-dir/link",
      }
      return config
  },
```

I think the following Pull Request in Next.js is related.

https://github.com/vercel/next.js/pull/73019
